quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"We sent it [Quran] down on the Night of Destiny"
  97,2,And what will make you comprehend what the Night of Destiny is
  97,3,The Night of Destiny is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"on that night, the angels and the Spirit come down by the permission of their Lord with His decrees for all matters"
  97,5,it is all peace till the break of dawn